snippet.title: Amber’s Adventures - Watersprite Lake Hike/Backpacking
snippet.description:
Ever heard of Watersprite Lake?
We made our way up to this gorgeous hidden spot, situated deep into the woods behind the Chief, Squamish, BC.
Watch our antics as we explore the mountains and surroundings of Watersprite Lake!
________________

Be Fearless! Be Free! BeWild!
